{"tid":2392843,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"我還傻傻等到short squeeze出現的那一天。","createTime":"2021-02-03T05:15:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-03T08:03:41.000Z","uid":38189,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"500a34ed04ded47e485797b61623ff79db62e165","tid":2392843,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T05:15:01.000Z","msg":"想用富途牛牛買入股票　好讓服務費能減少一點<br />\n死機的滋味　妳不懂這種感覺　用銀行買股票的妳永遠不會<br />\n<br />\n看華爾街在我面前　證明散戶們只是愚昧<br />\n妳不懂散戶　那些憔悴　是妳永遠不曾過的體會<br />\n<br />\n為什要sh gme妳永遠不了解<br />\n我又何苦勉強淡友愛上妳的一切<br />\n大鱷狠狠逼退　我的防備<br />\n靜靜關上門來默數我的淚<br />\n<br />\n明知道散戶贏到仆街不可能會<br />\n我還傻傻等到short squeeze出現的那一天<br />\n直到那一天　妳會發現<br />\n真正sh的人準備反cup<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n更多更詳盡歌詞 在&nbsp;※ <a href=\"http://Mojim.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FMojim.com&d=FM8PVMPbIH5fyb1BVmxPrdUsrLV3ynd9sCeqRx8pZcg%3D&h=ccf49826\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Mojim.com</a>　魔鏡歌詞網"},{"pid":"519fb7b626dfce2464cc7975e9318f70592804b5","tid":2392843,"uid":199081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T05:15:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11a5108afd3bab069ab3c4a957a69f13445cbb5c","tid":2392843,"uid":222390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T05:15:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79eff11b2b17efb1c374fe900c327cf043e85167","tid":2392843,"uid":1354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T05:15:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9d9a12cf0667fe7e7f68c32cc16597b6c7ffc66","tid":2392843,"uid":234509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T05:15:34.000Z","msg":"咁高產？<img src=\"/assets/